        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-ink:#000000;--color-onyx-canvas:#212121;--color-frost-canvas:#f5f6f5;--color-gallery-white:#ffffff;--color-tangerine-flash:#d9462b;--color-rose-bloom:#e296bb;--font-trjn-davinci:Georgia,'Georgia Pro',serif;--font-helveticaneue-light:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;--font-neue-montreal:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif; background:var(--color-onyx-canvas); width:600px; padding:48px 32px 56px 32px; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:var(--font-neue-montreal);\">\n  <!-- Top right metadata -->\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:flex-end; margin-bottom:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue-montreal); font-size:12px; line-height:1.17; color:var(--color-gallery-white); letter-spacing:0.06em; opacity:0.7; margin-bottom:4px;\">CONCRETE CLUB</div>\n      <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue-montreal); font-size:12px; line-height:1.17; color:var(--color-gallery-white); letter-spacing:0.06em; opacity:0.7;\">STORY</div>\n      <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue-montreal); font-size:12px; line-height:1.17; color:var(--color-gallery-white); letter-spacing:0.06em; opacity:0.7;\">1–1</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Main text block left -->\n  <div style=\"max-width:340px; margin-bottom:40px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue-montreal); font-size:12px; line-height:1.6; color:var(--color-gallery-white); letter-spacing:0.04em; margin:0; text-transform:uppercase;\">WITH OVER 10 YEARS OF INDUSTRY EXPERIENCE,<br>I LIKE TO JOIN FORCES WITH MY ARTIST FRIENDS<br>TO REFINE THE BORDER BETWEEN DIGITAL AND<br>ANALOG WORLDS.</p>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Illustration placeholder (sketch-style figure) -->\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:center; margin:0 0 40px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"width:180px; height:120px; position:relative;\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 180 120\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        <!-- Simplified sketch figure -->\n        <ellipse cx=\"90\" cy=\"22\" rx=\"14\" ry=\"16\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\"/>\n        <line x1=\"90\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"75\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <line x1=\"85\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"55\" y2=\"100\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <line x1=\"85\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"105\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <line x1=\"90\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"62\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <line x1=\"90\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"118\" y2=\"58\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <!-- stripes on body -->\n        <line x1=\"83\" y1=\"42\" x2=\"81\" y2=\"54\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"0.7\" opacity=\"0.6\"/>\n        <line x1=\"87\" y1=\"41\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"56\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"0.7\" opacity=\"0.6\"/>\n        <line x1=\"91\" y1=\"41\" x2=\"89\" y2=\"57\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"0.7\" opacity=\"0.6\"/>\n        <line x1=\"95\" y1=\"42\" x2=\"93\" y2=\"56\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"0.7\" opacity=\"0.6\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Second text block left -->\n  <div style=\"max-width:340px; margin-bottom:48px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue-montreal); font-size:12px; line-height:1.6; color:var(--color-gallery-white); letter-spacing:0.04em; margin:0; text-transform:uppercase;\">BASICALLY, INSTEAD OF HIRING AN AGENCY, YOU<br>GET TO WORK WITH A SELF-ORGANIZED TEAM OF<br>FRIENDS WHO ALREADY SPEND MOST OF THEIR<br>TIME TOGETHER.</p>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Collaborators block right-aligned -->\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:flex-end;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width:320px; text-align:left;\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue-montreal); font-size:12px; line-height:1.6; color:var(--color-gallery-white); letter-spacing:0.04em; margin:0; text-transform:uppercase;\">WE'VE COLLABORATED WITH BRANDS AND<br>STUDIOS SUCH AS ANTINOMY, ASHFALL, CHANEL,<br>LUFTHANSA, MCCANN NEW YORK, MICROSOFT,<br>TAMBIEN, PARIS SAINT-GERMAIN, PATTERN…</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
